<h3 style="color: #CC0000">THE OBEROI HOTEL</h3>            
An iconic 5 star hotel in New Delhi, The Oberoi offers a pleasant stay to its guests. Fully equipped with state-of-the-art amenities, the luxury hotel features plush interiors. A perfect blend of 220 rooms and suites inspired by the Lutyens’ New Delhi design, handpicked artwork and authentic furnishing win the heart of the guests.
Radiating luxury in every inch, The Oberoi cater the needs of travelers and business persons alike. Be spoilt for being served with 24*7 services which include a full time butler who is eager to serve you. Eat to your heart’s content at the Threesixty° main restaurant offering authentic cuisines. A memorable culinary experience awaits for you.
From temperature controlled wine cellar to the Cigar Lounge, the Oberoi has it all. Wellness Centre and Business Centre are also the part of the luxury hotel which allow you to travel without compromising with work and wellness.

<h3 style="color: #CC0000">THE OBEROI AMARVILAS HOTEL</h3>  
Oberoi Amar Vilas is part of one of India’s best hotel brands Oberoi hotels and resorts. Located in Agra, the hotel offers best view of the greatest monument of love - Taj Mahal; as it lies merely 600 m from the great structure. Architecturally, the hotel is inspired by Moorish and Mughal culture and its rooms, balconies, lawns, fountains, terraces and pavilions take you back to the regal times of Emperors and Princesses. The hotel is a great hit among tourists because of the majestic view that it offers of the Taj Mahal, especially at night.
Rich interiors of the hotel are complimented by best in class amenities and services that keep patrons rejuvenated, relaxed and pampered. Hotel is equipped Wi-Fi internet access in all rooms and public areas, 24 hour business center, fitness center, full service Oberoi spa, meeting and conference hall facilities, outdoor swimming pool, beauty parlor, baby sitting services, travel desk, electronic safe deposit boxes and 24 hour personal butler to cater to each and every need that a client might have. Apart from this the hotel also offers complimentary golf cart transfer to and from the Taj Mahal for site-seeing.One of the many highlights of Oberoi Amar Vilas is the Spa – which is run by trained Thai therapists who help patrons revitalize and reenergize with help of personalized treatments based on ancient Ayurveda, traditional Thai techniques and even western options. Over the years, hotel has earned numerous awards and recognitions both Indian as well as global; that reflect their commitment towards client centric hospitality. 

